  <entry>
    <title>起篇04</title>
    <link href="https://github.com/Simark-west/mouxi.github.io/2020/10/05/%E8%B5%B7%E7%AF%8704/"/>
    <id>https://github.com/Simark-west/mouxi.github.io/2020/10/05/%E8%B5%B7%E7%AF%8704/</id>
    <published>2020-10-05T15:53:17.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-10-09T14:35:51.344Z</updated>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;原本以为只是增加一项招待宾客内容的亲族宴会，丹朱也并没有特意穿着隆重的缁撮锦衣出席，仍旧是平日玩闹的纻衣纁裳。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这样的打扮方便他随时能溜王宫跑去乡野玩耍。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
